Entry Level Software Developer

Atlantictranstrading

- Boston, MA

AtlanticTransTrading is seeking entry level Software Developers to join our team who are enthusiastic passionate about coding, designing, and to play a key role in identifying solutions.
Responsibilities:
· Design, develop, code, and debug, document, support programs for low-volume transactions.
· Responsible for the development and support of the application used in agile methodology.
· Involve in the creation, general system design and technical specifications for new systems.
· Assist in preparing detailed and low level coding standards to facilitate the development.
Requirements:
· Bachelors or Master's degree in Computer Science or any related field.
· Good Knowledge on Application Development using SDLC using methodologies like Waterfall and Agile.
· Strong programming and debugging skills using Java, C++, C# or Python.
· Strong problem solving, analytical ability and interpersonal skills.
Job Type: Full-time
Salary: $65,000.00 to $75,000.00 /year
